{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10NordicMesh18TransactionMessagePAAE08continueC0Sbvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:10NordicMesh21LightHSLSaturationSetV","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"continueTransaction","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"extendedModule":"NordicMesh"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSet\/continueTransaction","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSet"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"more seconds earlier."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslsaturationset\/continuetransaction"]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLSaturationSet":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSet","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"LightHSLSaturationSet","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslsaturationset","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightHSLSaturationSet"}],"title":"LightHSLSaturationSet","type":"topic"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLSaturationSet/continueTransaction":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSet\/continueTransaction","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslsaturationset\/continuetransaction","abstract":[{"text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"continueTransaction"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s: